{"tid":2385482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美心餅店麻糬包藏壁虎被罰款9000元","createTime":"2021-01-29T05:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T10:21:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":284,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8aeb8acb8e4a44afbefa91f1dc6de6d6af9080","tid":2385482,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"屯門蝴蝶廣場的美心餅店，有麵包被發現有壁虎，美心承認食物的品質與購買人所要求者不符罪，屯門裁判法院判罰款9000元。 一名男顧客前年10月，在餅店購買麻糬包進食，發現裡面有一條壁虎，事後向餅店及當局投訴。美心說，已找滅蟲公司清潔及增加巡查原材料狀況，確保製作過程無異物。"},{"pid":"b2ae346fc4adebd26869182796c24a580c3171ab","tid":2385482,"uid":54126,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"送蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67703fe4320eaf07a4cb75c499706abf9fb13262","tid":2385482,"uid":47080,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"George 做乜咁傻入美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d96e926a776bb4f3094090c3ff5815764a33aa","tid":2385482,"uid":21545,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"食美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0aa3c5a1ea91af3526acc8ab04f099b6c11f57c","tid":2385482,"uid":40763,"like":8,"dislike":67,"score":-59,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"咁都告到？<br />\n食食下飯有隻甲由<br />\n又可以告？"},{"pid":"db12d853ad3e3a1236c8299608716a78819ce592","tid":2385482,"uid":89006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021